Class LocalSparkTrainable

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.simiacryptus.mindseye.eval.SparkTrainable
      • com.simiacryptus.mindseye.eval.LocalSparkTrainable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Trainable

    public class LocalSparkTrainable
extends SparkTrainable
    A debugging class which replaces SparkTrainable with an implementation that uses direct method calls instead of RMI. This can be useful for debugging in some situations.
